parameters: \N<Man>P-Please help me! Lend me a hand!

\N<Man>A comrade who entered the ruins with me has been injured and
can't move! Can you help me carry him to safety?

\N<Man>Are you going to abandon a person in need!? You heartless
fiend!
\N<Segi>...Understood. Please lead the way to this person.

\N<Segi>A poisonous plant for transdermal toxins... I wonder if this
is it.
